headline: General Motors Company (GM) Raises Its Dividend Rate by 20%
summary: General Motors Company (NYSE:GM) is one of the Best Cheap Stocks to Buy Right Now. As part of GM’s Q4-2025 earnings press release on January 27, the company announced a $0.03 per share increase in its quarterly dividend rate. This represents a 20% increase, bringing quarterly dividends to $0.18 per share and annual dividends to $0.72. […]
